SpoonerPlacements.Note: Blaine County has so much to offer a sightseer from the big city: hills, valleys, rocky coasts, degenerate rural townships and a world-famous diversity of communicable disease. If you want all the highs and lows with none of the itches and nosebleeds, this track is for you. Point to point Transform Race starting on Motorcycles, also featuring the Besra, Blazer Aqua, Zentorno and Trophy Truck.
